Replaces:	 
Breaks: 	gxsm3 (<< 3.54.0-0ubuntu3),
		gxsm4 (<< 4.2.1)
Description: Multi-channel data acquisition via STM/AFM
 GXSM -- Gnome X Scanning Microscopy.
 --- netcdf thumbnailer ---
 This small tool allows you to get a thumbnail 
 of *.nc in your favorite file explorer
 The thumbnailer works for netcdf files generated
 with GXSM3 and GXSM4 
